title: 'I'm not at all concerned": Trump on Sessions being questioned by special counsel
text:
'I'm not at all concerned": Trump on Sessions being questioned by special counsel 7:12am IST - 00:28 
President Donald Trump said he was 'not at all concerned' when asked by a reporter about Attorney General Jeff Sessions' reported interview with the special counsel's office investigating potential collusion between Russia and President Donald Trump's 2016 presidential campaign. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
